title: Exolaunch is ready to deploy over 30 smallsats on SpaceX’s Transporter-8 rideshare mission
summary: Exolaunch has completed the integration of 32 customer satellites, including those from ICEYE, for SpaceX’s Transporter-8 rideshare mission. The launch is scheduled for June 12 and marks Exolaunch’s 11th mission with SpaceX under long-term agreements. ICEYE is mentioned as a longstanding customer but no concrete deal or financial transaction is described.
